title: Feasibility Study — Solar Microgrid for North Industrial Park
meta: | type: study | ref: FS-2025-02 | date: 2025-03-10

section: Executive Summary
text: This study evaluates a 4.2 MWp solar microgrid with 6 MWh battery storage. The project clears the hurdle rate and is recommended for detailed design.

section: Key Metrics
metric: LCOE | value: 0.061 | unit: USD/kWh | target: 0.075 | trend: down | period: 25-year
metric: IRR | value: 11.4 | unit: % | target: 8.0 | trend: up | period: 25-year
metric: Payback | value: 7.8 | unit: years | target: 10 | trend: down | period: project-life

section: Assumptions
- Capex 6.8M USD
- Grid electricity price escalation 3.0% per year
- Capacity factor 21.5%

